➜考生网报志愿这些一定要看！！！
http://www.sohu.com/a/411352410_100023701	10828
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200804/c9a3239126a446bc90947ce790d163e2.gif" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200804/c9a3239126a446bc90947ce790d163e2.gif" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200804/c9a3239126a446bc90947ce790d163e2.gif" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200804/e918d4e43bad48e0869f09ef4066c29a.gif" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
